OL,3,CThe home-made weapons being used to
OL,4,Ctarget farms and livestock
OL,6,FFarmers say vandals are creating
OL,7,Frudimentary weapons designed to ruin
OL,8,Fmachinery and injure livestock.
OL,10,FHelen Smith, who has a dairy farm near
OL,11,FRotherham, said she had been
OL,12,Frepeatedly targeted by criminals
OL,13,Fcausing damage and in some cases
OL,14,Fkilling animals with no apparent
OL,15,Fmotive.
OL,17,FShe showed ITV News concrete blocks
OL,18,Fwhich had been set with large nails
OL,19,Fand left strewn in the fields of the
OL,20,Ffarm.
