OL,3,CThe home-made weapons being used to
OL,4,Ctarget farms and livestock
OL,6,F"There's thought going into it - it's
OL,7,Fnot just kids fooling about," she said.
OL,9,F"We've had no end of trouble - we've
OL,10,Fhad a cow shot with a bullet rifle,
OL,11,Fwhich was left overnight and we found
OL,12,Fit the next morning, dead, which was
OL,13,Fhorrendous to find.
OL,15,F"And then we've had concrete which has
OL,16,Fbeen made in plant pot holders, with
OL,17,Fsix-inch nails to puncture tyres and
OL,18,Ffor the cows to tread on and become
OL,19,Flame. We have people cutting the
OL,20,Fbarbed wire to let cows out."
