OL,6,FMrs Smith said her farm had been
OL,7,Ftargeted by arsonists in the past and
OL,8,Fshe had suffered personal attacks.
OL,10,F"I've been shot at before, I've been
OL,11,Fassaulted," she said. "We've had cows
OL,12,Fbeaten up with golf clubs and blinded."
OL,14,FInsurer NFU Mutual's Rural Crime
OL,15,FReport estimated that the cost of
OL,16,Frural crime last year was almost
OL,17,F#53million - a rise of 4.3% on 2022.
