OL,6,FMrs Smith said the impact on her
OL,7,Fcattle had more widespread
OL,8,Fconsequences. She said: "It has a
OL,9,Fknock-on effect down the food chain
OL,10,Fbecause they're not producing the
OL,11,Fmilk, there's no beef, there's no
OL,12,Fcalves. So the financial loss is
OL,13,Ftremendous."
OL,15,FA nearby farmer has suffered thousands
OL,16,Fof pounds worth of damage to fields
OL,17,Fcaused by illegal quad bikers.
