OL,4,Ctarget farms and livestock
OL,6,FThe man, who did not want to be named,
OL,7,Fsaid: "You need to understand what
OL,8,Fdamage this is doing to people in your
OL,9,Farea.
OL,11,F"In my opinion it is getting worse and
OL,12,Fthe more readily available quad bikes
OL,13,Fare becoming and motorbikes are
OL,14,Fbecoming. People just don't have the
OL,15,Fsame respect for what's not theirs."
OL,17,FSouth Yorkshire Police said it was
OL,18,F"committed" to tackling the problem of
OL,19,Foff-road bikes in Rotherham, with
OL,20,Fofficers carrying out regular patrols
OL,21,Fin hotspot areas.
