OL,6,FRotherham South Neighbourhood Policing
OL,7,FTeam Inspector Christopher Scanlon
OL,8,Fsaid: "Not only do these anti-social
OL,9,Fdrivers cause serious criminal damage
OL,10,Fto local landowners, but they also
OL,11,Fhave a negative impact on wildlife and
OL,12,Fthe local community. We are constantly
OL,13,Fmonitoring the situation and have run
OL,14,Foperations with the help of the
OL,15,Fforce's Motorcycle and Rural Crime
OL,16,FTeam to tackle this problem, with more
OL,17,Fdays of action planned in the future."
